-- Morgan Stanley, 3i Will Purchase HSBC Eversholt Rail Unit for $3.3 Billion
-- B y   C o l i n   K e a t i n g e
-- 2010-11-04T14:52:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-04/hsbc-agrees-3-4-billion-sale-of-eversholt-rail-group-to-investment-group.html
HSBC Holdings Plc said it agreed the
sale of Eversholt Rail Group to Eversholt Investment Group, a
consortium consisting of investment funds managed by 3i
Infrastructure plc, Morgan Stanley Infrastructure Partners and
STAR Capital Partners.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net  